description.en: Omni is a never-been-done-before mega app, that's full of world-class features and tools. Inside the app, you can go live, share stories, create channels, chat with other users, transfer money, video or audio call, sell or buy products in stores, create videos and photos with special effects and much more. Be a part of designing the future. Omni is more than just social media, it's a platform that empowers creators to have full ownership and control over their careers. Omni is the future.
